Class RoundTextFieldUI

  • java.lang.Object
    • javax.swing.plaf.ComponentUI

  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    javax.swing.text.ViewFactory

    public class RoundTextFieldUI
extends javax.swing.plaf.basic.BasicTextFieldUI
    A TextFieldUI that features rounded horizontal endpoints.

    Also if the JTextField has the client property "useSearchIcon" defined, this may place a magnifying glass icon in the left edge of this UI before the text.
